Package: nepalcensus
Type: Package
Title: Nepal Population and Housing Census 2021 Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Binoj", "Jung Bogati",
    email = "bjungbogati@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tidy access to tabular data from the Nepal Population
    and Housing Census 2021 (NPHC 2078 BS), conducted by the National
    Statistics Office (NSO) of Nepal. Contains 89 datasets covering
    household characteristics (housing, water, sanitation, lighting, absent
    population) and individual-level demographics (age, sex, education,
    marital status, disability, migration, fertility, economic activity,
    occupation, and industry), cross-tabulated by province, district, and
    local level (Gaunpalika/Nagarpalika). Includes helper functions to
    browse and search the data catalog.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
LazyDataCompression: xz
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Suggests:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/bjungbogati/nepalcensus
BugReports: https://github.com/bjungbogati/nepalcensus/issues
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
